    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. CFD model successfully predicts relative hemolysis index within acceptance criteria across all 5 CPB operating points and correctly identifies worst-case conditions. The assessment team reviewed the solver version discrepancy (validation conducted under ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 versus released build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7) and determined the single-patch delta introduces no material difference in solver behavior, citing the vendor change log which lists only documentation and installer corrections. On this basis the evidence is considered applicable to the model of record and the COU is accepted at Medium assurance level.",
